28
00:02:33,386 --> 00:02:36,514
Frank. Frank!

29
00:02:36,590 --> 00:02:39,423
- Get your hands off me!
- Francis, stop it!

30
00:02:39,493 --> 00:02:41,427
- Settle down.
- Let go of him.

31
00:02:41,495 --> 00:02:45,454
- Let go of me!
- Francis, just...
Take your hands off of him!

32
00:02:45,532 --> 00:02:48,797
- Listen to me, you little...
