It's outta here!

55
00:05:04,371 --> 00:05:08,239
- [Yelling]
- Frank, put it down! Frank!

56
00:05:08,308 --> 00:05:10,742
Come on!

57
00:05:10,810 --> 00:05:13,142
- It's a corker down the pipe!
- Frank, what's goin' on?

58
00:05:14,581 --> 00:05:17,448
- Frank, what the hell are you doing?
- [Yelling]

59
00:05:17,517 --> 00:05:20,680
- It's outta here!
- Talk to me. Tell me what happened.

60
00:05:29,429 --> 00:05:32,193
I just don't cut the mustard.

61
00:05:32,265 --> 00:05:35,291
Come on. Let's go.

62
00:05:35,368 --> 00:05:37,836
