63
00:05:40,106 --> 00:05:42,404
Chuck!

64
00:05:42,475 --> 00:05:44,466
Chuck!

65
00:05:46,946 --> 00:05:48,880
- Gieg!
- What?

66
00:05:51,651 --> 00:05:53,676
Oh, you...

