Get him up.

82
00:06:48,241 --> 00:06:51,176
Get him outta here.
Get him outta here.

83
00:07:08,595 --> 00:07:11,621
Do you remember the last time
you and I danced?

84
00:07:11,698 --> 00:07:14,132
