00:19:09,582 --> 00:19:12,574
Turn around.

224
00:19:18,257 --> 00:19:20,817
Ow! Ow.

225
00:19:20,893 --> 00:19:24,488
Ow.
[Groans]

226
00:19:27,066 --> 00:19:29,864
Hold that.

227
00:19:29,935 --> 00:19:32,096
- Next!
- [Groaning]

228
00:19:35,441 --> 00:19:38,774
Robert! Drop your pants.

229
00:19:41,847 --> 00:19:43,781
Way to go, Valentino.

