What do you make of it, Skipper?

233
00:19:56,462 --> 00:19:58,987
"Venceremos."

234
00:19:59,064 --> 00:20:00,998
Cubans.

235
00:20:01,066 --> 00:20:03,398
I'll get the horn.

236
00:20:05,404 --> 00:20:08,134
Jesus! She's got guns.

237
00:20:08,207 --> 00:20:11,836
