- Get down! Everybody down!

238
00:20:15,147 --> 00:20:18,810
Run up the colors.
We're Americans, damn it! Shay!

239
00:20:18,884 --> 00:20:21,444
Run up the colors!

240
00:20:22,988 --> 00:20:24,785
Jesus Christ!
Are they gonna sink us?

241
00:20:24,857 --> 00:20:29,191
- Take in all sail! Do it now.
- Sails down! Get going! Go on!

242
00:20:36,402 --> 00:20:40,930
- Here's the horn, Skipper.
- Who the hell do they think they are?

243
00:20:45,044 --> 00:20:47,137
[Commander Speaking Spanish]

244
00:20:47,212 --> 00:20:50,079
